sequenceDiagram
    participant Workload as EC2/Service in Private Subnet
    participant RT as Private Route Table
    participant NAT as NAT Gateway
    participant IGW as Internet Gateway
    participant Internet as Internet

    Workload->>RT: 0.0.0.0/0
    RT->>NAT: Forward outbound traffic
    NAT->>IGW: Send translated traffic
    IGW->>Internet: Outbound connection
    Internet-->>IGW: Response
    IGW-->>NAT: Return path
    NAT-->>Workload: Established outbound response only